flowchart TB
    subgraph L0["Process Supervision"]
      SD["supervisord\ninside container"]
    end

    subgraph L1["Service Process"]
      SV["server.ts / dist/server.js"]
      MG["singularity-supervisor-manager\n(timer in server)"]
    end

    subgraph L1B["Gateway Process"]
      GW["openclaw-gateway\n(separate docker compose service)"]
    end

    subgraph L2["Project Auto Flow Process"]
      SS["scripts/singularity-supervisor.mjs start"]
      CW["supervisor core watch loop\n(single current-project process)"]
      AD["singularity-flow adapter"]
      RT["project/runtime/supervisor.json"]
      PID["project/runtime/supervisor.pid"]
    end

    subgraph L3["Agents"]
      M["singularity-main"]
      R["singularity-reviewer"]
      W["singularity-writer"]
    end

    subgraph L4["Project State"]
      CP["CURRENT_PROJECT"]
      ST["status.md"]
      IL["interaction_log.md"]
      HO["handoff.md"]
      OUT["output.md"]
      DR["draft_review_history.md"]
    end

    subgraph L5["Docs Manager"]
      DM["docs-manager-executor.mjs"]
      DOCS["docs project\n05_delivery/final_article.md"]
    end

    subgraph L6["User Interaction"]
      U["User / Editor"]
      TG["Telegram group"]
    end

    SD -->|autorestart server| SV
    SV --> MG
    SV -->|proxy + health check only| GW

    MG -->|every 15s| CP
    CP -->|resolve current project id| ST

    MG -->|if current project\nworkflow_mode=auto\nand step=5 or 7| SS
    SS -->|ensure one watcher for\ncurrent project| CW
    CW --> RT
    CW --> PID
    CW --> ST
    CW --> AD

    AD -->|step_5 +\nnext_actor=reviewer| R
    AD -->|step_5 +\nnext_actor=main\nand awaiting_user_choice=yes| M
    AD -->|step_7 +\nnext_actor=writer| W
    AD -->|step_7 +\nnext_actor=reviewer| R
    AD -->|step_7 +\nnext_actor=main| M

    U --> TG
    TG --> M
    TG --> R
    TG --> W

    M --> ST
    M --> IL
    M --> HO
    M --> OUT

    R --> ST
    R --> IL
    R --> DR

    W --> ST
    W --> OUT
    W --> DR

    MG -->|if docs_publish_requested=yes\nfor current project| DM
    DM --> DOCS
    DM -->|write publish result| ST
